Steps.Message: Update at 20:40 - We're sorry for the power cut tonight, our engineers are on their way to investigate. At this point we think the issue is an underground cable fault that initially interrupted power to 1444 properties. However, by rerouting electricity in the area, currently 608 customers are still affected. Using an average timescale, we're estimating power will be on between 23:00 and 00:00, but this may change later depending on what our engineers find. Power back on? To stop receiving texts, please just send CANCEL to 80876 (standard text fees apply).

We became aware of this power cut at 20:28. We’re sorry for any disruption this may have caused you. We didn’t know in advance there would be a power cut, but now that we know, our teams will do everything they can to get your power back quickly. Engineers in our control room have switched some customers power back on in your area. To get everyone’s power back on we may need to attend to investigate and make repairs. We’ll continue to update you until everyone’s power is back on.
Steps.Name: We are restoring customers automatically

Steps.Message: We have engineers on their way. As this is affecting your area, they will not need to attend your property. Rest assured once they arrive, they’ll work as quickly as is safely possible to get your power back on.
Steps.Name: Engineers on their way
